2) Crested Spaulders... see above.<br>
3) 6/65 rings.<br>
4) Deepwater Boots, Fine Plate Boots, Imbued Field Plate Boots, Enchanted Full Plate Boots.<br>
5) Imbued Field Plate Bracer &amp; Imbued Field Plate Vambraces if you want the nice look... otherwise go with Enchanted Full Plate.  Silver, Gold or maybe Electrum.<br>
