<br>
fingers: upgrade at least 1 ring to velium fire opal. Start working on the coldain ring quests. If you are interested in the chardok rings by the time you hit 50, you may wish to spend lots of time bashing goblins in Droga, Nurga and FM. More details <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.geocities.com/saleani/">here</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.<br>
<br>
feet: Boots of Ro (ac 11, hp 35), if you are patient, brave and can get into pick up groups in Maidens Eye, there are shrouded boots (ac 12, cha+5 all other stats +4) which drop from the coterie (undead). Deepwater would be nice, but on my server, they sell for about 2k.<br>
<br>
face: I am fond of either Tribal mask (looted in chardok) or cougarskin mask (quest item). <p><a href='http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=64195'>Combat Profile</a><br>
